data.description: 2007 single family home on 10 acres that is secluded yet directly off of Hwy 7.  Davis school district.  2604 sq ft living space with new 2 year old class 4 shingles.  3 bed with walk in closets in 2 of bedrooms and the other with 2 step in closets.  2 bathroom both with double sinks and master bath with jet tub/stand up shower/private toilet area/extra walk in closet.  house has vaulted ceilings and rounded moldings throughout and lots of storage.  Has open floor plan to kitchen/living/dining room, separate laundry room,  game room with window unit that is both AC/heat.  house is total electric with stainless steel microwave, dishwasher and oven.  has wrap around lighted porch with extra patio area off of back porch.  Has aerobic septic sprinkler system, rural water and many mature pecan trees.  33ft above ground pool with a 5 section deck with child resistant lockout gate.  36x40 barn with 16ft lean-to that is insulated and has metal covering both inside and out of barn with electricity, heated water, a walk through door and 2 overhead doors.  Also has a 12/24 shed with top to bottom shelving and has an oversized 2 car carport measuring 24x25x9ft that is covered on 3 sides.
